    {
      "id": "bridge-runtime-smoke-overview",
      "type": "markdown",
      "label": "Instructions",
      "position": {
        "x": -1267.8269873885833,
        "y": -347.2937709012896
      },
      "width": 500,
      "height": 240,
      "visible": true,
      "showLabel": true,
      "data": {
        "markdown": "## Bridge Runtime Smoke Test\n\nThis graph compares two otherwise-identical API nodes that were stamped with different bridge grants.\n\n1. Select `Create-only API Node` and run it.\n2. It should be blocked with a `BRIDGE_RUNTIME_REQUIRED` diagnostic.\n3. Select `Runtime API Node` and run it.\n4. It should execute and fetch `/library/documentation/OnboardLLM.md`.\n\nThe two bridge nodes above them should also show the authority difference directly in their grant chips.",
        "_classBinding": {
          "key": "markdown",
          "sourceRef": "github://twilite-zone/public/library/classes/nodes/markdown.node-class.node",
          "ref": "github://twilite-zone/public/library/classes/nodes/markdown.node-class.node",
          "identity": {
